{"content": "<h2>The Artist: TrailMix</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>With the expansive natural beauty of Boulder, Colorado at his backdoor, TrailMix finds his inspiration on the paths of nature. Once the adventure is over, glitch switches the scene to something more akin to computer vision. Alpha Centauri Kid saw the vision and picked up 'The Climber' followed shortly by MintFace acquiring 'The Summit' in March 2022.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"352\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/the-summit-TrailMix-1024x481.gif\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/the-summit-TrailMix-1024x481.gif 1024w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/the-summit-TrailMix-300x141.gif 300w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/the-summit-TrailMix-768x361.gif 768w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/the-summit-TrailMix-1536x722.gif 1536w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/the-summit-TrailMix-2048x963.gif 2048w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/the-summit-TrailMix-1320x620.gif 1320w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/the-summit-TrailMix-600x282.gif 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>The Summit by TrailMix collected by MintFace</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t<blockquote>\n\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\"Nature is code. Seeking out Source.\"\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<cite>TrailMix</cite>\n\t\t\t\t\t</blockquote>\n\t\t\t<h2>The Collection: Long Walks</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>Long Walks showed a broader range of glitched out landscapes that will test even the best GPUs. The calm of nature stirred up with errant pixels of wayward colors seems like a new pathway forward for photography and glitch. The titles are as much a story as the scenes themselves. 'Deathless, Reborn', 'A Sailboat in the Middle of the Ocean', 'Pismo in the Evening' and \"I'm Not Going to Get Lost.'</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"595\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/trailmix-glitch-long-walks-1024x813.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/trailmix-glitch-long-walks-1024x813.png 1024w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/trailmix-glitch-long-walks-300x238.png 300w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/trailmix-glitch-long-walks-768x610.png 768w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/trailmix-glitch-long-walks-1536x1220.png 1536w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/trailmix-glitch-long-walks-1320x1048.png 1320w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/trailmix-glitch-long-walks-600x476.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/trailmix-glitch-long-walks.png 1574w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>Long Walks collection by TrailMix</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t<h2>A Specific Artwork: If Only I Knew</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>The tidal flow peters out on the edge of its magnetic pull and the beginning of the mass of earth. 'If Only I Knew' is a 1 of 10 edition that collectoors could mint if they found their way to the minting page. There is an out of phase serenity to watching a body of water filter its way forward through a comb of animation.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"999\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/If-Only-I-Knew-TrailMix.gif\" alt=\"\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>If Only I Knew by TrailMix</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>"}